<view class="page-shell"><view class="custom-nav" style="padding-top: {{navTop}}px; height: {{navHeight}}px;"><view class="back-button" bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}" mode="aspectFit" /><text>校园管理</text></view></view><scroll-view class="page-scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height: {{navSpacer}}px;"></view><view class="content"><view class="page-heading"><text>赛事内容发布确认</text><text>确认赛事内容与发布设置</text></view><view class="publish-card"><text class="label">赛事名称</text><view class="event-title"><text>U10班级对抗赛</text><text>已完赛</text></view><view class="score-card" style="background-image:url({{court}})"><view><text>🏀</text><text>橙队</text></view><view><text><text>38</text> : 34</text><text>比赛结束</text></view><view><text>🏀</text><text>黑队</text></view><view class="mvp"><text>本场MVP</text><image src="{{mvp}}" mode="aspectFill" /><text>林浩</text><text>★ 18分 6篮板 4助攻</text></view></view><text class="block-title">发布内容</text><view class="content-list"><view wx:for="{{contents}}" wx:key="label"><view>▤</view><view><text>{{item.label}}</text><text>{{item.caption}}</text></view><text>✓</text></view></view><text class="block-title">可见范围</text><view class="scope-grid"><view class="{{item.activeClass}}" wx:for="{{scopes}}" wx:key="key" data-key="{{item.key}}" bindtap="selectScope"><text>{{item.label}}　○</text><text>{{item.caption}}</text></view></view><view class="privacy">🔒 未授权照片不公开　<text>仅发布已获得授权的照片，保护孩子隐私</text></view><text class="block-title">配文预览</text><view class="caption-preview"><image src="{{court}}" mode="aspectFill" /><text>U10班级对抗赛圆满落幕！双方小球员全力以赴，比分胶着，精彩不断。恭喜橙队获得胜利！每一次拼搏，都是成长的印记！<text>#U10班级对抗赛 #成长在赛场</text></text></view></view><view class="bottom-actions"><button bindtap="saveDraft">▤ 保存草稿</button><button bindtap="publish">➤ 确认发布</button></view><view class="safe-space"></view></view></scroll-view></view>
